OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FTesco chair to quit after  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fclaims over behaviour      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, John Allan is stepping down as chairman
OL,6, of Tesco following allegations over his
OL,7, conduct.                               
OL,9,FMr Allan, who is also a former         
OL,10,Fpresident of the CBI business lobby    
OL,11,Fgroup, has strongly denied three of    
OL,12,Ffour claims made against him.          
OL,14,FHowever, board member Byron Grote, who 
OL,15,Fwill temporarily replace Mr Allan as   
OL,16,Fchairman, said: "These allegations risk
OL,17,Fbecoming a distraction to Tesco."      
OL,19,FTesco said it had made "no findings of 
OL,20,Fwrongdoing".                           
